Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一直被監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫老胡和蘭芳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道又失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一不注意就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又倒在路邊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳根清淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家 有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}戰友的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 來探望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大佐給的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 抽煙的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 贏過一回嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這個遊戲太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 半夜的話可以去砍人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 至少把霍克愛大姐帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回頭和大姐說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要監視他到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們捲進這麼危險的任務 真是對不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍務方面不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你是因病請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果被一般市民或我們的軍隊相關人員發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想簡單了事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有前途一片光明的話題？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交上女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬家遇見麻煩的時候 她對我很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 超好的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把那個女的砍了會不會很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是餓倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 從清國來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼從那大老遠的地方跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你的入國許可證呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非法入國者要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在路邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對餓倒在路邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們就先去軍部露個臉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我就先去休斯家打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早點看看克蕾西亞和艾莉西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我們馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 過會見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 休斯中佐有沒有替我們收集賢者之石的情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被大總統禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把我們入手的情報告訴他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐應該在軍法會議所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳拿著那邊的鑰匙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 是三號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用過後就這麼放著沒收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我只是去拿需要的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻去收拾 請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我等會來拿 麻煩妳快點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離軍隊會議沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 也許是我多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還是不要太逞強多休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是馬斯坦古大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好 佛卡大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼大佐會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書庫也開著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 其實那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是被大佐強行要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當沒看見好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 大佐在調查什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐問我有沒有第五研究所的相關資料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 休斯准將的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是准將介紹我到這裡工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有一堆工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 謝絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南邊遇上了點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到愛力克兄弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是去見達普利斯的師傅 偶然碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴他們休斯已經去世了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所和賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭的材料是活生生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙習慣管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插手愛力克兄弟在調查的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了不應該知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和自身的事件有關導致休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩兄弟知道的話 心靈會受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你調查得真徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定隔牆有耳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克愛中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉在的話 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大佐會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月開始我轉到中央工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你今天幹什麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微收集一下情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外想去和休斯中佐打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回鄉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著老婆和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備繼承家業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想見他一面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為太過於心急 而做魯莽的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在這種時候把他們當孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於那對兄弟來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進的路障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們總有一天會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒資格說阿姆斯壯少佐是老好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一句老好人就能解決的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點通知溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經去休斯家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這麼急？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了休斯中佐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一堆話想和他說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少想和他說聲再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有收到通知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 全軍都給他送行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺人性化的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 也許你們已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他晉升兩級 不是中佐 是准將了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晉升兩級？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回鄉下了卻能晉升兩級？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 為什麼中佐會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯准將在愛德華出院後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被不明人物殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人還沒被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我把他捲進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再來中央都市的話 記得來打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯穿著鎧甲沒法吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還沒決定住處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受責備的人只有我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是哥哥一個人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們兩個人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然決定了無論發生什麼事都要取回身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人為此而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願放棄取回身體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要對克蕾西亞夫人說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我說？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉也來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫知道了賢者之石的一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的死 是犯人警告你們不要再繼續調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這完全是我們招來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救人而死 真像那個人的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前就是個愛管閒事愛操心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是幫了人家損了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我覺得他從來沒有後悔過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在臨死之時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說放棄之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫的死就會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使賢者之石不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還有別的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克蕾西亞夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用自己可以接受的方式前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食堂馬上要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的話 身體會吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘋果派？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後 我練習了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說出來像是自誇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比不上克蕾西亞夫人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想讓休斯先生嘗嘗的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐在調查休斯的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住什麼線索了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了方便監視 才把他調到了中央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓他乖乖待著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是重要的人柱候補
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從妳男朋友那裡打聽不出什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道他是天然呆還是老練
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去收集下情報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吃完了不收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 拉斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要火焰之大佐安分下來就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要試試另一個方法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼計策？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於吵鬧的狗 要給牠點食物才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞·羅斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是憲兵隊司令部的 亨利·達古拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說明一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們懷疑妳殺害了馬斯·休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會聽妳的辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞·羅斯少尉否認罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集這個人的相關資料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要隱秘行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 把這個花包一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:21:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索拉莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你 約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說些有趣的故事給我聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.61,0:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替罪羔羊被仇恨之火焰所焚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年受憎惡與後悔的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人把手伸向了黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17話 冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如同在看不見的手上跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:06.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:12.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:30.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:36.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:43.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:59.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:14.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:44.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.97,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:22:57.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:08.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:16.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:22.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:27.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:32.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:38.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:44.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:48.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:52.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:56.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠
